Package com.googlecode.cqengine.resultset.order

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttributeListComparator<O>
    A Comparator which can sort a collection of objects based on a list of Attributes referring to comparable fields within those objects.
    AttributeListComparators  
    InsertionSortedListBuilder
    Copies objects from a ResultSet into a List, using insertion sort to allow the resulting list to be built and sorted in a single pass.
    MaterializingOrderedResultSet<O>
    A ResultSet which wraps another ResultSet, providing an MaterializingOrderedResultSet.iterator() method which returns objects in sorted order according to a comparator supplied to the constructor of this ResultSet, and which never returns the same object more than once.
    MaterializingResultSet<O>
    Wraps another ResultSet and ensures that the Iterator returned by the MaterializingResultSet.iterator() method never returns the same object more than once.
    SimpleAttributeListComparator<O>
    An optimized comparator similar to AttributeListComparator, but efficiency-optimized for the case that all attributes are SimpleAttributes.
